It seems like the Windows builders can get "stuck" somehow, without producing any output for ~30 minutes or more: https://github.com/rust-lang-ci/rust/runs/1777375321

Is this a known issue?

Looks like a test never finished: test [ui] ui\consts\assoc_const_generic_impl.rs has been running for over 60 seconds
I tried running that locally a bunch of times, but it always completed quickly.
